posting_body: ['We are open for business!', 'We are now offering in person tours Monday-Saturday.', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Welcome to Legacy', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 123', 'OR Text', '123', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact us.', 'This is a 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath, approximately 1529 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Here at our Pflugerville rental homes, we offer three exceptional floor plans with three and four-bedroom options that all come with spacious 2 car attached garages to choose from.', 'You will be delighted with custom features including hardwood floors, pantry, central air and heating, walk-in closets, and extra storage.', 'Prepare gourmet meals in your fully-equipped kitchen with white speckled or slate grey quartz countertops, farm white or trendy grey cabinetry, crisp clean white subway tile backsplash, stainless steel whirlpool energy-efficient appliances, and smart Honeywell thermostats you can monitor from anywhere in the world.', 'Features:', 'Stand Alone Homes, Front Yard and Fenced Private Back Yards, Irrigation Water Sensors, Washer and Dryer Connections, Gas Range, 2 Inch Faux Wood Blinds, Wood Flooring, Stainless Steel Whirlpool Energy Efficient Appliances, LED Lighting, 2 Car Attached Garage, White Subway Tile Backsplash, Farm White or Trendy Grey Cabinetry, White Speckled or Slate Grey Quartz Countertops, Stand Up Showers, Smart Thermostats', '*In Select Rental Homes', 'Community Amenities:', 'Hassle Free Lawncare, On-site Professional Management, Resort-style Swimming Pool, Park and Picnic Areas with Barbecue Grills, On-site Professional Maintenance, Amenity Center and Clubhouse with Wi-Fi, Fitness Center', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets Welcome Upon Approval.', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', '5wwLmox85BM']
